<eesti> c) projektip&otilde;hiselt tehtud ettepanekud audiovisuaalteoste v&auml;ljat&ouml;&ouml;tamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise> The selection criteria will take account chiefly of the European and international nature of the projects, in particular of their: </inglise>
