<inglise> Prior appraisal, monitoring and subsequent evaluation </inglise>
<eesti> Eelhindamine, j&auml;relevalve ja j&auml;relhindamine </eesti>
<inglise> Prior to approving a request for Community support, the Commission will carefully evaluate it to check that it complies with this Decision and with the conditions set out in subsections 2 and 3 of this section of the Annex. </inglise>
<eesti> Enne kui &uuml;henduse toetuse saamistaotlus kinnitatakse, kontrollib komisjon seda hoolega, et veenduda, kas see vastab k&auml;esolevale otsusele ja k&auml;esoleva punkti alapunktides 2 ja 3 s&auml;testatud tingimustele. </eesti>
<inglise> Requests for Community support must include the following: </inglise>
<eesti> &Uuml;henduse toetuse saamistaotlused peavad sisaldama j&auml;rgmist: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) a financial plan setting out all the project funding components, including the financial support requested from the Commission; </inglise>
<eesti> a) rahastamiskava, milles esitatakse k&otilde;ik projekti rahastamise komponendid, sealhulgas &uuml;henduselt taotletav rahaline toetus; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) a provisional work timetable; </inglise>
